                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>New York</placeName>\n                <date>17th April 1864</date>\n            </p>\n            <p>\n                <addressee>Revd I Leeser</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p>Dear Friend,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">I have delayed this<lb/> long replying to your last two\n                let<lb/>-ters, hoping to get sufficient time<lb/> to pay <persName>Mrs\n                    Lawrence</persName> a visit that<lb/> I might speak to her about your<lb/>\n                various publications; but as I have<lb/> yet not been able to do so, I will<lb/> no\n                longer defer thanking you for<lb/> the kind manner in which you<lb/> responded to\n                our appeal, &amp; beg to<lb/> inform you that every thing has been<lb/> accomplished\n                to our entire satisfaction<lb/> through your kind introduction to</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3mp4w778/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
