                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>you and trust you will accept<lb/> the enclosed Twenty Five Dollars<lb/> as a portion\n                of the same, the receipt<lb/> of which please acknowledge by post</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Hoping to have the pleasure<lb/> of seeing you on your next\n                visit<lb/> to this city, I remain,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(11)\">Yours respectfly</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(11)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">J. Palache</persName>\n            </p>\n            <pb n=\"Envelope\"/>\n            <p>THE <persName>MISSES PALACHE'S</persName></p>\n            <p>FRENCH &amp; ENGLISH</p>\n            <p>BOARDING &amp; DAY SCHOOL,</p>\n            <p><placeName>No. 174 West 37th St.</placeName>,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\"><placeName>NEW YORK</placeName>.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">To The <addressee>Revd I Leeser</addressee></p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <placeName>No 1227 Walnut St</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">\n                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">\n                <placeName>Penn</placeName>\n            </p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
